sequenceDiagram
  participant U as Usuario
  participant C as Client Component
  participant S as Server Action
  participant A as Auth custom
  participant DB as Supabase Postgres
  U->>C: altera placar do jogo
  C->>S: salvarPalpite(matchId, placar)
  S->>A: validar cookie de sessao
  A->>DB: buscar session_token_hash valido
  DB-->>A: usuario autenticado
  S->>DB: atualizar predictions jsonb
  DB-->>S: registro salvo
  S->>S: revalidatePath('/palpites')
  S-->>C: sucesso + total parcial
  C-->>U: feedback visual
